<p>Seeing a spring of water in a dream indicates good things, an abundance of money, and other meanings. We will mention the interpretations for the single, married, pregnant, divorced, and male, like watering with spring water, or water coming out of the spring, or drinking water from hot springs, or water coming out of the rock for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a> and others, continuously. The topic:</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of seeing a spring with water in a dream</span></h2>
<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-العين-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=722" > Seeing a spring </a> with water in a dream is a blessing, goodness, prosperity, and the fulfillment of a wish if the dreamer hides it. Whoever sees springs of water erupting in his house and he is not afraid, will suffer a calamity. May God protect us and you.  That his family members will cry.</p>
<p>Whoever sees that he is making ablution from a spring of water, this indicates that the dreamer will be healed, whether the water is clean or not, whether it is hot or cold, as long as it is pure, and it is permissible to make ablution with it for prayer due to the ablution.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
