<p>Whoever sees in his house or in an inappropriate place that a spring of water has erupted, this indicates that the dreamer will acquire sustenance, goodness, and benefit, and if it comes down in his house, this is sadness from women.<br/>And if it erupts from a wall, it is worry that will befall him from a man in that house, like a brother or brother-in-law or friend, and if it breaks in and comes out of the house until everything is gone, he will escape from worry quickly, and if it does not come out, the worry will remain.  And if it is pure, it is concern for a healthy body, and he hates from the eye of whoever erupts from his spring and his water does not flow.<br/>And if he sees a spring of water flowing to his owner in a limited stream, and whether his owner is alive or dead, then its interpretation is good in his religion and his work, and this goodness will continue until <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-يوم-القيامة-في-المنام?page=3697" > the Day of Resurrection </a>.<br/>Whoever sees a spring of water erupting in a place or a house, overflowing or not overflowing, then it will be sadness and crying.  It is then more serious and stronger.<br/>And they said: Whoever sees that it has erupted in his house or in a place of water, he will buy a servant. And if he sees eyes erupting from the earth, then the people of the place will increase in money.  And fruits.<br/>And the water that flows from the valleys, if it is pure, is a sign of goodness for all people, especially the sick and the poor, as it seems to be ease and innocence because it is not more delicious than water.</p>
<p>Whoever washes with spring water, if he is distressed, God will comfort him, or he is afraid or sick, or he will be healed, or he has debt, or he will pay off his debt, or he has sins, God will atone for them.  For him.</p>
<p>Whoever sees a clear spring, his owner's money will increase. And if he sees it flowing into houses, then it is a happy life for the common people.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
