</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>As for whoever sees in a dream a clear spring flowing over his house, this is sustenance and goodness that it will give him.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of water springs in the dream of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a></span></h2>
<p>The interpreter of dreams, <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ابن-سيرين-في-المنام?page=1665" > Ibn Sirin </a>, stated that springs represent in the <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/عالم-الأحلام?page=2180" > world of dreams </a> some crucial aspects of your destiny or indicate that you are facing some life-changing situations in the future.</p>
<p>Dreaming of springs or eyes made of water indicates concerns about your future, and this vision also indicates that you have to make important decisions about your future.<br/><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-عين-الماء-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=7" > The spring of water </a> that then develops and becomes like a river symbolizes the inner strength that the dreamer has to achieve his goal.<br/>On the other hand, the clear spring of water indicates purity and hope, while the dirty spring of water indicates the lack of clarity of your goal.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
