</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>In general, when you see a source of water such as <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-عين-الماء-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=7" > the spring of water </a> in your dream, this dream symbolizes enthusiasm, and this vision shows that you are the person who cares a lot about true values ​​and tries to live a dignified life.<br/>And sometimes the <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-عين-الماء-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=7" > spring of water </a> appears in the dream that the fortune-teller relies heavily on the desire not to harm anyone when making his important decisions, because you prefer to suffer from injustice than to apply it to <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شخص-ما-في-المنام?page=2395" > someone </a>.</p>
<p>When you see a mysterious spring of water whose owner you do not know, this dream indicates that there is a possibility of failure because you cannot achieve everything you want, which makes you feel weak and may continue to feel sorry for yourself. You didn't do anything to change the situation that makes you unhappy.</p>
<p>When you drink from a well of water, this dream indicates that you are taking a chance on your opportunities, and you may get a job that you have always dreamed of, and you will realize that these opportunities are rare in your life, and you will do everything to show yourself. The best possible performance.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
