<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of the spring in a dream</span></h2>
<p>Seeing a spring in a dream is good news, as seeing a spring indicates that the dreamer will achieve a great living and goodness in his life in general, especially in his social life.<br/>The spring in a dream means that the dreamer will meet again with people whose relationship was broken before, and this will make him very happy, and he will be able to achieve all his dreams and desires in a short time and will realize a quick recovery from any. Diseases that he suffers from.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of seeing a source of water in a dream</span></h2>
<p>The source of water in a dream indicates that the owner of the vision will adhere to a friend who will greatly help him change his practical plan and help him follow other ways to greatly increase his financial income.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شرب-الماء-في-المنام?page=3294" > drinking water </a> from the spring in a dream</span></h2>
