<p>Seeing a clear spring of water in a dream represents the presence of a dear friend in the dreamer's life.  This friend is ready to give up everything for the happiness of his friend and protect him until death.<br/>Seeing yourself drinking from a clear spring of water in a dream indicates a brave, kind-hearted, and good-spoken person.</p>
