<p><span></span></p>
<p>Seeing the person you love in a dream means that you will live happily and that the person will receive good news that will relieve him from his state of weakness.</p>
<p>Whoever sees the person he loves means that there will be positive developments in his private life and thanks to the bilateral dialogues his problems will be solved.</p>
<p>For a married woman, it indicates a beautiful love life and they will see all the beauty of life through their relationship.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
