</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Seeing the loved one in a dream means fulfilling the life that the person has longed for for years and desires and he will <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-حمل-طفل?page=129" > bear a child </a> and make his parents happy and start a new stage in his life.</p>
<p>The unmarried girl who sees the person she loves means that they will love at first sight and will meet someone they will not be able to get out of their minds.<br/>This vision also indicates the end of the person's suffocating and sad situations, and also indicates that his wealth will laugh at him, his split will open, and the door to his desires will open.</p>
<p>Seeing the person you love in a dream is one of the visions that represents the subconscious mind of people who dream of marrying someone they are attached to and love, and they think about him all the time during their day. It generally indicates the loved one who always comes to the visionary's mind and always makes his memories alive with him.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
